      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FLYING MONKEY'S (3) goes very well this course and distance starting 16 times for six wins and seven minors. Recorded a 1.5 lengths win (22.81) in a Grade 5 last time at this track. Rates on top and should go close. SPEEDY HOUDINI (1) found some support last start but struggled into seventh (23.75), beaten 6 lengths. Was in the money the start prior. Some good form is emerging from her last run. Cannot be taken lightly. HOW HIGH SPIKE (7) turned in a better run last time to find a minor placing (23.57) at this track behind Blazing Warrior in a Grade 4/5. Chased the leaders and with a clean run can be prominent. The form out of last race has been strong. Leading player again. RATTLIN' IMPACT (2) gets a chance to improve on an unplaced run at his latest outing at this circuit.",
